snippet.title: SynthVR 1.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
SynthVR is a modular synthesizer for virtual reality.

Get it for PCVR:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1517890/SynthVR/

Get it for Oculus Quest:
https://sidequestvr.com/app/1203

The music in this trailer was made and recorded in SynthVR, then mixed in Ableton Live. Watch the original patch being created in this live stream:
https://youtu.be/URqKfUCYwyQ

Try out this patch yourself using access code 0098 in the app's "Discovery" tab.
